{"tid":2254480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京：不排除將來與中國建立軍事同盟","createTime":"2020-10-23T00:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T09:06:53.000Z","uid":91914,"like":290,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"16f2f402538574081590aa9148b90c989fb0756f","tid":2254480,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:47:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】俄羅斯總統普京表示，不排除會同中國建立軍事同盟。<br />\n<br />\n普京以視像形式參與莫斯科一個國際論壇，他表示由俄羅斯和美國決定全球重大議題的時代已經過去，美國、英國和法國的影響力逐漸減弱，同一時間中國和德國在政治和經濟的份量正在邁向超級強國。<br />\n<br />\n普京表示，中俄目前沒有需要建立軍事同盟，但不排除將來有這樣的可能。雙方舉行過多次軍事活動，標誌兩國軍事合作的發展，俄羅斯又分享敏感的軍事技術增強了中國的軍事潛力和防禦能力，未來兩國的軍事聯擊亦會更加緊密。<br />\n<br />\n中俄德朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a7868728350cdde69aa1fca011732f40ba7643","tid":2254480,"uid":261913,"like":186,"dislike":3,"score":183,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:48:31.000Z","msg":"唔建立軍事同盟 點會有機會係後門突入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6054f0929cf9a87de2983acbcffb10dfa0804fbf","tid":2254480,"uid":30988,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"乜未結嘅咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db1c3fe641fd7c37170629e9e37e07919c62e2e","tid":2254480,"uid":66087,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"支持美國賣多d武器比烏克蘭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546eca4a9ffbf7782567c357e3f80b13d567b148","tid":2254480,"uid":184679,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:52:51.000Z","msg":"普京：不排除任期滿後辭去總統職位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b3e68dab62c13cf9be794e73f84a81ecaa6835","tid":2254480,"uid":103916,"like":47,"dislike"